from Soup: 23 The best fit to the experimental results of Liu et al. 28 includes zero SEI resistivity. To ensure that this parameter choice, which simplifies computation substantially, does not interfere with the accuracy of the results, simulations were performed with a non-zero resistance. Results are shown in figure 4 . The SEI resistance lowers the output voltage, but has little effect on capacity fade.
